Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: 1301 & 1315 Inkster Boulevard can be sold together or separately.  This is an excellent opportunity with Inkster Boulevard exposure and fenced compound/expansion space to accommodate most industrial users.  Direct access to Inkster Boulevard, drive aisles on each side of both buildings and over 130’ of rear yard depth allows for easy truck access and maneuverability.  Together, 1301 & 1315 Inkster provides ±0.9 acres of existing yard/fenced compound space.
